Second version to my first map "Fy_dusk" which can be found in my submissions panel under my profile. 

-Change log-

->Added some cover, you asked for it you got it ;]
->Added more props and stuff to "play around with" into the map
->Added some light posts to the map to give it a more "parkish" feel
->Added env_sun to the map to make it look better
->Fixed some bugs in the map, cant remember them all =/

(Story of the map)

While a train was on its way delivering some cargo, a sudden earthquake happened causing a major wreak and leaving a huge gap in the ground. All passengers die,except a select few. your running out of food, and water. Will you shoot your fellow survivors and eat them alive....after all you do have to live don't you?
